# INPUT message: FORWARD+LEFT buttons, yaw=3.14159, pitch=-0.5
# Buttons: FORWARD|LEFT = 0x01|0x04 = 0x05
# yaw=3.14159 (~pi): 0xd0 0x0f 0x49 0x40 (little-endian float32)
# pitch=-0.5: 0x00 0x00 0x00 0xbf (little-endian float32)
# Wire format: [type(1)][size(2)][buttons(1)][yaw(4)][pitch(4)] = 13 bytes
00 0d 00 05 d0 0f 49 40 00 00 00 bf 00
